sudo apt-get install mingw32

wget http://icculus.org/~dolson/sdl/sdl-cross-install.sh
./sdl-cross-install.sh


This line should work to cross-compile:
PATH=/opt/SDL-1.2.13/bin:$PATH ./configure --target=i586-mingw32msvc --host=i586-mingw32msvc --build=i586-linux


Reference:

http://icculus.org/~dolson/sdl/
http://www.astro.gla.ac.uk/~paulm/Cross/
